# web-nav-qwen2.5vl-7b — max-context light model for Nanobrowser on big/complex pages.
#
# Use when web-nav-qwen2.5-coder-14b (16k ctx) "loses" elements on large DOMs — e.g. it
# read only the top of a Wikipedia infobox and mis-extracted a lower field. qwen2.5vl:7b is
# only 6 GB, so it fits a full 32k context on the 12 GB GPU (double the coder model's room),
# which keeps the whole element tree in view. It is also a vision model, so Nanobrowser's
# screenshot/vision mode CAN be enabled with it (optional).
#
# temperature 0.2: near-deterministic actions.
#
# As with the coder model: point Nanobrowser's Planner, Navigator, AND Validator all at this
# one model so Ollama keeps it resident (no ~13 s reload per re-plan).
FROM qwen2.5vl:7b
PARAMETER num_ctx 32768
PARAMETER temperature 0.2
